6. Chunking

Chunking (psychology)

The brain compresses information into chunks.

Example:

149217761945 → hard
1492 1776 1945 → easy

Pantheon use

Organize knowledge into modular packets:
	•	Concept Cards
	•	Daemons
	•	Modules
	•	Invariants

This matches your Pantheon modular architecture.

